{"tid":540716,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)懲罰者1-2","createTime":"2018-01-25T17:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T20:28:22.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"135cfc03f241e0f8b67f5119a563c289198c44c4","tid":540716,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bw%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=a59ed9a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bw%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=33a19439\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://b0.rimg.tw/samuel1711/77d7e8ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fb0.rimg.tw%2Fsamuel1711%2F77d7e8ba.jpg&h=7caa812b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg/220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FPunisherwarzoneteaser.jpg%2F220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg&h=08597fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特（托馬斯&middot;簡Thomas Jane 飾）的生命中，絕大部分時間都在於死神賽跑。早年在海軍陸戰隊服役，退役後又進入FBI。在槍砲火光中生活了多年之後，弗蘭克不願再整日收到死亡的威脅，家人整日為他擔驚受怕。所以，他決定提前退休與妻兒享受平靜的生活。可是，在最後的一次任務中，卻因意外使一名無辜青年死亡。而這名青年的父親卻是坦帕市的大富商霍華德&middot;桑特（約翰&middot;特拉沃塔John Travolta 飾）。為了給兒子報仇..<br />\n<br />\n2.本想歸隱田園，與家人共度天倫的FBI探員弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特，無奈的在黑幫殺掉妻<br />\n兒之後走向了黑暗復仇的不歸路。弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特大難不死，在悲痛過後開始成為這個城市裡隱秘的&ldquo;懲罰者&rdquo;，在黑暗中打擊那些猖狂的犯罪分子的頭號先鋒。在處決了城內走私行當的龍頭老大之後，懲罰者的名聲鵲起，因此也令城內不少罪犯聞風喪膽，而他也就繼續穿著代表懲罰者的骷髏制服，穿梭在這個充滿罪惡的都市中.....<br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bw%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=404f94ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bw%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f676ee11\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d9f6f1e9a481e7d0e2ae89c8bbfc9bda248c6d","tid":540716,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763e861040c384d520f995f99829f9cfc5751a61","tid":540716,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7576d8ec8856d3e4af754182143aa6e1edc44d","tid":540716,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /